definition.value: An all-trans-polyprenyl diphosphate composed from eight isoprenyl units.
A monocarboxylic acid that is acetic acid in which one of the methyl hydrogens has been replaced by a halogen atom.
An oxo dicarboxylic acid comprising adipic acid having the oxo group at the 3-position as well as a hydroxy substituent at the 2-position.
